0:02:21.450,0:02:24.733
It's exactly because she has your trust
that I must treat her generously.

0:02:25.040,0:02:28.160
How about granting her the title of Attendant, just like when you entered the palace?

0:02:28.480,0:02:30.680
I'll name her Attendant Xi [Auspicious].

0:02:33.295,0:02:34.640
Your Majesty, I dare not ...

0:02:34.640,0:02:36.684
How could I deserve the honor of serving Your Majesty?

0:02:36.920,0:02:38.324
I beg Your Majesty to forgive me.

0:02:39.460,0:02:40.546
How strange.

0:02:41.220,0:02:44.640
Any maid in the palace would thank the Buddha
for receiving such favor and honor,

0:02:45.140,0:02:46.190
but you’re not willing.

0:02:46.190,0:02:47.577
I admit my offense, Your Majesty.

0:02:47.800,0:02:48.960
I already ...

0:02:49.715,0:02:51.236
have someone in my heart.

0:02:52.300,0:02:54.240
You have someone in your heart?

0:02:55.280,0:02:57.709
A guard, or an imperial doctor? Tell me.

0:02:58.260,0:03:00.900
If this marriage is fated, I will decree it.

0:03:02.620,0:03:04.320
I want to keep Jade by my side

0:03:04.440,0:03:06.493
until the day I arrange her marriage myself.

0:03:08.060,0:03:08.900
Jade.

0:03:09.220,0:03:10.760
Bring Hongyan from the Imperial Nursery.

0:03:10.760,0:03:11.780
His Majesty wants to see him.

0:03:11.780,0:03:12.393
Yes.

0:03:19.800,0:03:21.873
I like to see you being jealous.

0:03:23.660,0:03:25.580
Since Consort Vertu passed,

0:03:25.680,0:03:27.154
your heart has been heavy.

0:03:27.660,0:03:30.000
It’s rare to hear a few lighthearted words from you.

0:03:30.520,0:03:32.899
My sorrow is not the most important thing.

0:03:33.500,0:03:35.599
Gūwalgiya "created winds and waves" in the harem,

0:03:35.599,0:03:38.980
which caused Meizhuang's prenatal shock 
and then bleeding to death.

0:03:38.980,0:03:40.220
Don’t worry.

0:03:40.940,0:03:43.131
I will respond to this in time.

0:03:44.260,0:03:45.313
I hope so.

0:03:46.620,0:03:48.504
Or Meizhuang still won't be able to close her eyes

0:03:48.750,0:03:50.189
"under the Yellow Springs."

0:03:50.720,0:03:52.086
At the court this morning,

0:03:53.000,0:03:55.200
Gūwalgiya Emin said since I have four sons,

0:03:55.260,0:03:57.460
I should consider designating the eldest as Crown Prince,

0:03:57.460,0:03:58.540
to consolidate the nation's foundation.

0:03:58.540,0:04:00.930
Whoever suggested that should be flogged at court immediately.

0:04:00.930,0:04:02.400
Even flogging to death isn’t too harsh!

0:04:03.740,0:04:05.390
Your Majesty is in your prime.

0:04:05.390,0:04:07.120
Why mention the nation's foundation right now?

0:04:07.880,0:04:09.160
That’s extremely inappropriate.

0:04:09.160,0:04:10.944
Being designated as Crown Prince too early

0:04:11.560,0:04:13.711
means being a target to all.

0:04:14.520,0:04:18.660
It would encourage the princes to have their eyes upon the crown

0:04:19.320,0:04:21.980
instead of concentrating on their studies.

0:04:23.420,0:04:25.980
Furthermore, our tradition is to select
the most virtuous, not simply the eldest.

0:04:26.080,0:04:28.445
Why "wag their tongues" about their ages?

0:04:29.206,0:04:30.080
By the way,

0:04:30.460,0:04:32.700
the Fourth Prince has been diligent in his studies.

0:04:32.920,0:04:35.320
Has Your Majesty questioned him on his schoolwork?

0:04:36.180,0:04:38.771
He's all right. He can answer quite smoothly.

0:04:40.000,0:04:41.120
However,

0:04:41.280,0:04:43.133
I believe our child will be better -

0:04:43.380,0:04:44.738
Hongyan will be even better.

0:04:45.260,0:04:47.700
The Empress has a gentle heart.

0:04:48.592,0:04:52.480
She made the unwise decision to add alum
to the water for the blood droplet test

0:04:52.480,0:04:53.760
to confuse the others,

0:04:54.300,0:04:56.913
largely because Your Majesty favors the youngest son so much.

0:04:57.660,0:05:00.000
Even now, I’m frightened when I recall that day.

0:05:00.280,0:05:02.940
So I request Your Majesty be less partial to Hongyan.

0:05:03.960,0:05:06.940
The Empress was worried. I understand that.

0:05:08.280,0:05:10.151
Although Hongshi isn’t outstanding,

0:05:10.320,0:05:12.700
how could I not care for him? He’s also my child.

0:05:14.420,0:05:17.300
I’d better appoint a marriage for him,

0:05:17.940,0:05:20.040
which may also relieve the Empress's unease.

0:05:23.240,0:05:25.506
I haven’t yet dared tell Imperial Mother that

0:05:27.240,0:05:29.970
the Empress also took part in that incident.

0:05:31.220,0:05:34.491
She secretly changed the water for the blood droplet test,

0:05:34.820,0:05:37.213
conspiring to frame the Noble Consort and the Sixth Prince.

0:05:37.420,0:05:38.931
You don’t need to tell me.

0:05:39.940,0:05:40.960
These days,

0:05:41.400,0:05:43.760
you won't take a single step into her palace.

0:05:44.600,0:05:46.560
In my heart, I already "knew the numbers."

0:05:47.120,0:05:49.189
Since the Noble Consort got pregnant and returned,

0:05:49.400,0:05:54.400
even I had a shadow of misgiving in my mind, 
let alone other people.

0:05:55.400,0:05:58.615
The imperial bloodline must be pure.

0:05:59.322,0:06:00.900
Not a hint of doubt can be allowed.

0:06:02.180,0:06:03.822
The Empress manages the palace affairs.

0:06:03.822,0:06:05.750
She’s obliged to investigate.

0:06:06.960,0:06:09.640
The blood testing method was at fault -

0:06:10.560,0:06:13.068
since the water was easily contaminated with alum -

0:06:13.580,0:06:15.622
and that nearly wrongly accused the Noble Consort.

0:06:15.960,0:06:18.480
Emperor, you can blame her for incompetence,

0:06:19.480,0:06:22.020
but you cannot accuse her of conspiracy.

0:06:24.150,0:06:24.959
I know.

0:06:25.740,0:06:27.200
Not for any other reason,

0:06:27.990,0:06:31.200
but because she is the sister of your most beloved.

0:06:32.250,0:06:34.663
You can distrust Yixiu,

0:06:35.380,0:06:37.960
but you can't distrust Première.

0:06:38.340,0:06:39.096
True.

0:06:39.500,0:06:41.521
The Empress is the mother of the country.

0:06:42.880,0:06:45.600
The people are uneasy when the mother of the country is uneasy.

0:06:46.930,0:06:51.509
If the Emperor always appears
with a favored concubine instead of the Empress,

0:06:52.843,0:06:55.837
that concubine may harbor ideas of reaching beyond her station.

0:06:56.560,0:07:00.400
If one day, a concubine rises above the Empress,

0:07:02.070,0:07:07.721
then the imperial harem, even the 
entire country, will be in chaos.

0:07:09.450,0:07:10.206
Yes.

0:07:12.870,0:07:15.780
"One's words are kinder when death is nearer."

0:07:17.370,0:07:19.162
I'm near the end of my life.

0:07:20.710,0:07:23.200
You need to remember, Emperor,

0:07:24.015,0:07:28.859
no matter how good your Noble Consort is,
there is only one Empress.

0:07:42.570,0:07:43.610
Elder Sister!

0:07:44.150,0:07:47.680
We come to the garden every day, 
either to see the flowers or net butterflies.

0:07:47.700,0:07:49.565
I'm getting so bored!

0:07:52.740,0:07:56.840
Outsiders think the Forbidden City is full of 
unlimited imperial wealth and luxury.

0:07:57.080,0:07:59.836
Only insiders know there's no place more tedious

0:07:59.836,0:08:03.710
than the square-shaped sky inside these high walls.

0:08:03.710,0:08:04.710
Right?

0:08:07.800,0:08:10.090
What are you two sisters talking about?

0:08:10.390,0:08:11.640
Sounds like a lively discussion.

0:08:11.640,0:08:13.620
- Peace and grace to Your Majesty.
- Peace to Your Majesty.

0:08:23.980,0:08:26.284
My sister-in-law is here too. What a coincidence!

0:08:26.440,0:08:27.515
I thank Your Majesty.

0:08:31.240,0:08:34.032
 The weather is getting hotter lately.

0:08:34.490,0:08:36.341
Are you accustomed to living in the palace?

0:08:36.500,0:08:38.990
If there's any discomfort, just tell your sister.

0:08:39.370,0:08:41.176
Consider the palace as your home.

0:08:41.460,0:08:43.560
Yurao has stayed in the palace for quite some time now.

0:08:43.750,0:08:46.879
Although living in the palace is different from at home,
she's gotten used to it.

0:08:47.260,0:08:50.302
There was some good first-flush Dragon Well tea
offered as a tribute.

0:08:51.390,0:08:52.609
I'll send some to you.

0:08:52.760,0:08:54.241
I wonder if your sister likes it.

0:08:54.470,0:08:55.930
I thank Your Majesty for caring.

0:08:55.930,0:08:57.713
Everything in the palace is grand and majestic,

0:08:57.890,0:08:59.320
with beautiful ladies in abundance.

0:08:59.320,0:09:02.504
Everything is extraordinary, 
except that I always have to obey the rules.

0:09:02.810,0:09:05.440
Unlike at home, where I have no rules.

0:09:05.770,0:09:09.920
For example, in ordinary families, 
I would call you my brother-in-law.

0:09:10.110,0:09:13.429
However, in the palace, I must always remember that

0:09:13.429,0:09:15.863
Your Majesty has heavenly authority and I musn't give offense.

0:09:16.030,0:09:18.200
I have to be prudent and cautious all the time,

0:09:18.200,0:09:20.000
so, the palace doesn't feel like home.

0:09:20.460,0:09:21.504
Listen to that!

0:09:24.170,0:09:26.639
You have great rhetorical skills.

0:09:26.840,0:09:30.080
But compared to your sister, I'm afraid you have to admit defeat.

0:09:31.380,0:09:34.550
Here she is: complaining that the palace
 is not as comfortable as home,

0:09:34.550,0:09:37.350
but, I just can't get upset with her.

0:09:37.970,0:09:40.194
I'm no match for Yurao's rhetorical skills.

0:09:40.980,0:09:46.543
I've been wondering what kind of future brother-in-law
 will be able to tame her sharp tongue.

0:09:47.320,0:09:49.702
Your sister just recently returned.

0:09:49.990,0:09:53.334
Why are you in such a hurry to marry her off?

0:09:54.660,0:10:00.000
I suggest she stay around for a couple more years
since she's still young.

0:10:00.450,0:10:02.620
She should take her time to select the best for her.

0:10:04.170,0:10:06.497
If my sister-in-law finds the palace too constraining,

0:10:07.210,0:10:10.743
I just remembered Yunxi came to the palace today, and

0:10:11.670,0:10:15.397
he suggested going to the Summer Palace for archery
since the weather is good.

0:10:16.180,0:10:19.472
Noble Consort Lumière, will you keep me company?

0:10:20.350,0:10:22.020
And my sister-in-law will join us too.

0:10:22.020,0:10:25.404
No matter who he is,
I'm not interested if he's not a good archer.

0:10:26.770,0:10:28.112
Yurao agrees to go.

0:10:28.440,0:10:29.940
Your Majesty's idea is wonderful.

0:10:29.940,0:10:32.300
It's a rare opportunity to see Venerable Prince Shen.

0:10:32.300,0:10:35.840
Please allow us to get changed before joining Your Majesty's procession.

0:10:36.780,0:10:37.620
Good.

0:11:40.720,0:11:41.566
Here.

0:12:14.880,0:12:15.840
Bravo!

0:12:38.570,0:12:42.120
Yunxi is getting better and better with his horseback archery.

0:12:43.030,0:12:47.600
Our father taught Yunli horseback archery personally,

0:12:47.950,0:12:50.000
but now he is so out of practice that

0:12:51.460,0:12:53.790
he is worse than when he was seven or eight.

0:12:55.300,0:12:56.480
Your Majesty,

0:12:56.710,0:13:00.200
I got rusty from "drinking alone with the moon" too much.

0:13:01.180,0:13:05.512
Whereas Your Majesty has assiduously maintained your skills in archery.

0:13:07.680,0:13:12.831
Our 17th brother is still not married.
When he is, his hands and feet will be even softer.

0:13:15.770,0:13:18.720
I wouldn't have drunk if I knew you were going to make fun of me.

0:13:18.990,0:13:21.890
I was already light-headed before shooting the arrow.

0:13:23.320,0:13:24.126
Fill up.

0:13:28.106,0:13:29.330
My offense deserves death.

0:13:29.330,0:13:31.584
Don't worry, it's just a piece of clothing.

0:13:32.120,0:13:33.945
I'll get changed in the side chamber.

0:13:37.590,0:13:38.720
What's that?

0:13:42.050,0:13:43.092
Give it to me.

0:14:01.150,0:14:04.820
Our 17th brother must have had a romance somewhere.

0:14:05.990,0:14:09.640
Otherwise he wouldn't carry a girl's trinket around!

0:14:29.890,0:14:31.360
This paper-cut portrait ...

0:14:32.100,0:14:34.310
looks like Noble Consort Lumière.

0:14:52.080,0:14:53.733
That's quite a resemblance.

0:14:54.830,0:14:56.630
Unfounded allegations -

0:14:56.630,0:14:58.710
I have experienced too many this year.

0:14:59.750,0:15:01.360
It is just a small portrait.

0:15:01.590,0:15:03.698
What makes Your Majesty think it is me?

0:15:05.300,0:15:07.472
This small image does look a bit like Noble Consort Lumière.

0:15:07.760,0:15:09.050
But doesn’t Your Majesty think

0:15:09.050,0:15:10.993
it also resembles Yurao or Jade?

0:15:13.980,0:15:16.937
The girl in the portrait looks happy and displeased at the same time.

0:15:17.230,0:15:19.520
The more I look at it, the more I think it resembles Yurao.

0:15:24.070,0:15:26.749
In a month it will be the Qixi Festival.
 [Chinese Valentine's Day]

0:15:26.950,0:15:29.230
Will Your Majesty give this story a happy ending?

0:15:31.080,0:15:32.200
But…

0:15:32.200,0:15:34.447
Yurao and Yunli just met for the first time.

0:15:57.560,0:16:02.397
The edges of this image are slightly discolored.

0:16:03.360,0:16:07.440
Yunli must have held it in his hand and looked at it many times.

0:16:09.490,0:16:12.080
My sister-in-law came to the palace a few months ago.

0:16:12.080,0:16:14.160
She didn’t met Yunli until today.

0:16:14.490,0:16:15.565
It’s not her.

0:16:26.210,0:16:28.320
I beg Your Majesty's forgiveness for my capital offense.

0:16:28.340,0:16:29.423
This ...

0:16:30.253,0:16:32.253
is my image.

0:16:35.060,0:16:36.097
Really?

0:16:38.100,0:16:40.000
It was seven years ago,

0:16:40.100,0:16:42.416
I put it in this tasseled sachet.

0:16:43.690,0:16:47.367
When Consort Fleur ordered Her Highness to be 
punished by kneeling in the Palace of Earthly Honor,

0:16:47.367,0:16:50.343
I met Lord XVII, so I asked him for help.

0:16:50.700,0:16:53.987
After that, I went to the Hall of Converging Light to extend my gratitude.

0:16:55.950,0:16:57.113
You did?

0:16:57.580,0:17:00.693
When I was in the Hall of Converging Light,

0:17:01.540,0:17:04.480
I saw some pieces of colored paper on the table.

0:17:04.590,0:17:07.222
On a whim, I cut some window flowers

0:17:07.380,0:17:09.125
as a thank-you gift for His Lordship.

0:17:09.550,0:17:13.460
Then, His Lordship asked me if I knew how to cut a portrait.

0:17:14.470,0:17:16.310
So I cut out an image in my own likeness

0:17:16.310,0:17:18.574
and put it into this sachet.

0:17:20.560,0:17:24.293
On another day, His Lordship met me.

0:17:24.770,0:17:26.940
He asked me my favorite flower, and

0:17:26.940,0:17:28.683
I told him I like pollia.

0:17:30.740,0:17:33.202
Your Majesty can see if there are

0:17:33.570,0:17:35.544
a few petals of pollia in the sachet.

0:17:45.630,0:17:46.913
Exactly so.

0:17:47.300,0:17:48.840
If it wasn't your image,

0:17:48.840,0:17:51.520
how would you know what is inside?

0:17:54.140,0:17:57.434
Huan Huan, have you known her heart?

0:17:59.310,0:18:00.960
I am such a fool.

0:18:01.060,0:18:03.840
She put herself through a lot hiding it from me.

0:18:05.060,0:18:08.089
I've noticed that you wear an azalea in your hair every day.

0:18:08.780,0:18:11.586
Why? Do you prefer azalea,

0:18:11.780,0:18:12.610
rather than pollia?

0:18:13.820,0:18:16.370
That is because His Lordship said that

0:18:16.370,0:18:18.200
I look pleasing with azalea blooms in my hair.

0:18:18.370,0:18:19.360
So…

0:18:20.000,0:18:20.800
So I ...

0:18:21.710,0:18:24.500
A few months ago, whenever I visited Consort Lumière’s palace,

0:18:24.500,0:18:25.960
I didn’t see Jade.

0:18:25.960,0:18:27.840
I heard that when Lord XVII was sick,

0:18:27.840,0:18:29.440
it was Jade who took care of him.

0:18:30.300,0:18:32.417
I was confused at the time.

0:18:33.050,0:18:35.505
It turns out there is this fated relationship!

0:18:36.090,0:18:38.040
No wonder.

0:18:38.080,0:18:42.200
That's why you dropped the tray in fright that day,

0:18:42.230,0:18:45.760
when I teased Noble Consort Lumière
that I would promote you to Attendant.

0:18:46.900,0:18:48.246
And that's also why,

0:18:48.730,0:18:51.487
Yunli never even considered having a Lord Consort.

0:18:52.150,0:18:55.180
Given my humble status, I dare not "climb on a high branch."

0:18:55.660,0:18:56.649
Yet...

0:18:57.620,0:19:01.600
I've heard that his Lordship's garden has 
planted plums with jade-colored blossoms.

0:19:02.500,0:19:04.540
I haven't had the honor to see them.

0:19:04.790,0:19:07.500
I only wish that I'll be able to look at them some day,

0:19:07.760,0:19:10.000
then I shall be happy and content.

0:19:11.050,0:19:13.068
If you two keep on waiting,

0:19:13.590,0:19:16.283
I'm afraid you'll be waiting for another seven years!

0:19:16.890,0:19:19.750
Here, today I'll make a ruling:

0:19:20.720,0:19:23.354
Jade is granted marriage with you.

0:19:23.520,0:19:24.270
Your Majesty -

0:19:24.270,0:19:26.562
Your Majesty, with my lowly status,

0:19:27.230,0:19:29.451
how do I deserve the honor to serve His Lordship?

0:19:29.650,0:19:31.649
If Yunli didn't tell you,

0:19:32.781,0:19:36.287
