I had only Jade and Jinxi to share the "frosts and storms."

0:20:24.540,0:20:27.716
Jade grew up with me, and we're as close as sisters.

0:20:28.120,0:20:31.680
Your Majesty, since His Lordship has cherished Jade for seven years,

0:20:31.880,0:20:35.235
I believe, it's because he didn't want her to be treated poorly.

0:20:35.590,0:20:37.130
What do you propose?

0:20:39.630,0:20:41.963
I request to take Jade as my honorary sister

0:20:41.963,0:20:43.489
and record her name in the pedigree book

0:20:43.489,0:20:45.640
as the second daughter of the Niohuru family,

0:20:45.640,0:20:48.940
