0:21:09.750,0:21:12.210
If you enter His Lordship's estate without a good title and name,

0:21:12.210,0:21:14.080
when people talk about this,

0:21:14.340,0:21:17.590
some may kindly say you've been cherished by His Lordship for years;

0:21:17.590,0:21:19.243
that your fate was granted.

0:21:19.243,0:21:21.975
But others may maliciously speak of pre-marital intercourse.

0:21:22.220,0:21:24.640
It will ruin both of your reputations for nothing.

0:21:27.600,0:21:28.644
Your Majesty,

0:21:29.230,0:21:32.180
please excuse my obstinence, but I cannot take Jade as my primary wife.

0:21:33.730,0:21:35.140
Many years ago,

0:21:35.570,0:21:36.850
I met a lady ...

0:21:37.360,0:21:38.725
our hearts were committed.

0:21:39.150,0:21:40.900
Later on, we were parted with a thousand miles between us,

0:21:40.900,0:21:42.400
and we weren't able to marry.

0:21:42.400,0:21:43.582
Yet in my heart,

0:21:44.521,0:21:46.240
she is my only wife.

0:21:47.490,0:21:48.857
Jade is a good girl,

0:21:49.500,0:21:51.740
but I can never take her as my primary wife.

0:21:54.250,0:21:56.924
I hope Noble Consort Lumière can understand.

0:21:58.800,0:22:00.469
I leave the decision to Your Majesty.

