Biding her time has left her as his only unmarried daughter.

0:27:54.490,0:27:57.920
When the news of you having a Lord Consort spread,

0:27:58.110,0:28:00.333
grief overcame her ...

0:28:00.823,0:28:02.372
and she's become

0:28:02.995,0:28:05.111
too ill to get out of bed.

