In a nobleman's marriage,

0:28:59.464,0:29:02.372
all other matters take precedence over a true heart.

0:29:02.800,0:29:04.600
I want you to marry her

0:29:04.600,0:29:08.317
to pacify the heart of a veteran official.

0:29:08.520,0:29:10.100
If you really don't like her,

0:29:10.730,0:29:12.852
consider it as keeping one more person at home.

0:29:13.150,0:29:15.881
Why let her illness take her life away?

0:29:16.650,0:29:21.400
If Duke of Pei develops a grudge because of this,

0:29:21.740,0:29:24.631
it's not good for the peace in the court.

0:29:25.200,0:29:26.738
If you say so,

0:29:26.990,0:29:28.800
I must provide for her for life.

0:29:29.068,0:29:31.080
I will treat her well.

