0:34:06.820,0:34:09.060
I feel deep consolation,

0:34:09.740,0:34:11.723
and don't hope for anything else.

0:34:12.660,0:34:14.299
Now that you're back,

0:34:14.990,0:34:17.514
I won't let you be sent back to the "barren hills and wild rivers."

