0:36:16.950,0:36:20.160
I don't have the time or the heart for regret.

0:36:21.240,0:36:24.640
Your future path is what you have chosen today.

0:36:25.540,0:36:28.341
I hope you will walk on without any regret.

0:36:29.580,0:36:31.200
Elder sister, I am afraid.

